<p class="ayah 65-6" id="6" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَسْكِنُوهُنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Lodge them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْ حَيْثُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[from] where</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَكَنتُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you dwell,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(out) of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وُجْدِكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your means</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and (do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُضَآرُّوهُنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">harm them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِتُضَيِّقُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to distress</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِنَّ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[on] them.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they are</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُوْلَـٰتِ حَمْلٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">pregnant,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَأَنفِقُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then spend</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">on them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَتَّىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">until</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَضَعْنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they deliver</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَمْلَهُنَّ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their burden.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَرْضَعْنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they suckle</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for you,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَـَٔـاتُوهُنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then give them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُجُورَهُنَّ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their payment,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأْتَمِرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and consult</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَيْنَكُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">among yourselves</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَعْرُوفٍ‌ۖ</span><span c