<p class="ayah 65-9" id="9" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَذَاقَتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So it tasted</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَبَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) bad consequence</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْرِهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) its affair,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَكَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and was</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَـٰقِبَةُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) end</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْرِهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) its affair</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خُسْرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">loss.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>9<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
