/span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>10<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 65-11" id="11" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَّسُولاً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">A Messenger</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَتْلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">reciting</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَايَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) Verses</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُبَيِّنَـٰتٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">clear,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّيُخْرِجَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that he may bring out</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَمِلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and do</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">righteous deeds</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class=